Release history for swall

next
  [Changed]
  - We now decide on a per-monitor basis whether an image will be tiled
    or scaled. This further simplifies the command line interface and
    allows for different tiles per monitor.
  - The threshold to detect tiles has been lowered to 60% of the
    monitor's size.

v17.10  2017-10-10
  - Initial release.
  - Set root wallpaper and handle the three most common cases.
